    "benefits": "There are two primary benefit to becoming an armoursmith. As someone who holds this rank, it is expected of them that they are knowledgeable on the subject and that their wares are of the best quality made with the best materials. With this in mind, armoursmiths can ask for a steeper price when selling their wares.\r\n\r\nFurthermore, an armoursmith often has priority over others when it comes to buying materials. Merchants are aware of the status that is tied to the rank and the profit they can make with their wares. Therefore, they prioritise the armoursmiths when they are selling quality materials, because the armoursmith will still pay a hefty price for it.",
